Subject: Error login for Published report for the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor
Description: Hello Support, may I know is there any settings need to be set to access the NEA web portal, as on the certification portal and helpcenter didn't specify what need to be done to login to the NEA web portal. please do assist thank you.
Solution_Comment__c:
The customer the ability to login using local windows account to Web Console of Netwrix Enterprise Server.

Solution:
Modified the file "WebServer.exe.config" present at "C:Program Files (x86)STEALTHbitsStealthAUDITWeb" with true value for ""WindowsAuthentication"
